<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>VANRANG TOI A PENGTU CH36</title>
<key>Ab</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Vanrang toi a pengtu na si, Ni le thla ah thatnak kan hmuh, Arfi zong
 kha kan hmuh ca ah, Na lianhngannak a lang ngaingai.

[V2]
 Keimah nunnak kha na si i, Ka kalnak lam kha na ceuter, Zantim caan ah
 arfi bangin, Na lawmhnak nih a kan ceuter.

[V3]
 Na hmai chiat kha kan zan a si, Na velngeihnak kan chun a si, Chun cha
 in zaangfahnak a lang, Sual khuadawm nih a phen kho lo.

[V4]
 Na biatak kha kannih kan pe, Luatnak le hnangamnak a si, Nang ca
 biaktheng kan lung cungah, Mei thiang pakhat lawng a ceu tiang.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>36</hymn_number>
</song>